/div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; flex-grow: 0; height: 12px; width: 16px; transform: translateY(-4px);"></div><div style=" width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 8px solid #F4F4F4; border-left: 8px solid transparent; transform: translateY(-4px) translateX(8px);"></div></div></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 24px;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 224px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 144px;"></div></div><p></p><p style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px; margin-bottom:0; margin-top:8px; overflow:hidden; padding:8px 0 7px; text-align:center; text-overflow:ellipsis; white-space:nowrap;"> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C6XimL-Rimz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none;" target="_blank">Slipknot (@slipknot) 分享的帖子</a></p></div></blockquote><p><script async src="//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js"></script></p><p>巴西金属偶像<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sepultura">Sepultura</a>的前鼓手 Eloy Casagrande 现在已被确认为 Slipknot 的新鼓手。上周，卡萨格兰德于 4 月 25 日 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-slipknot-perform-first-gig-with-new-drummer-3750966">在加州 Pappy + Harriet&#39;s 烧烤酒吧举行的</a>最后一刻亲密俱乐部演出中首次与乐队合作。这场惊喜演出是在 4 月 24 日 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-slipknot-perform-first-gig-with-new-drummer-3750966">演出日期前一天宣布的。</a> ，他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-slipknot-play-career-spanning-setlist-in-old-school-costumes-at-sick-new-world-2024-3751457">成为拉斯维加斯“病态新世界”音乐节的主角</a>。</p><p>在亲密的演出中，乐队穿上了 1999 年首次亮相时穿的经典红色连身裤。乐队的几位原始成员也戴上了复古面具，而新成员则展示了新面具。 </p><figure id="attachment_3594014" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3594014" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3594014" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/sepultura-eloy-casagrande@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/sepultura-eloy-casagrande@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/sepultura-eloy-casagrande@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/sepultura-eloy-casagrande@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/sepultura-eloy-casagrande@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/sepultura-eloy-casagrande@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/sepultura-eloy-casagrande@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3594014" class="wp-caption-text">前 Sepultura 鼓手 Eloy Casagrande。图片来源：MAURO PIMENTEL/法新社，盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>埃洛伊·卡萨格兰德 (Eloy Casagrande) 很快就担任活结乐队的鼓手，这让长期粉丝感到惊讶，他们自 2013 年以来一直关注乐队的无数阵容变化。通常情况下，乐队对新成员的身份非常保密，通常会让互联网侦探知道揭露身份，而不是仅仅揭露他们自己的身份。</p><p>到目前为止，活结乐队中只有一名成员的身份尚未得到确认或透露。去年取代长期成员克雷格·琼斯后，他们的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-are-seemingly-teasing-a-new-member-3452721">新键盘手和采样器的身份仍然是个谜</a>。</p><p>自从 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sepultura-drummer-quits-band-ahead-of-final-tour-3594013">今年早些时候宣布退出巴西乐队</a>以来，埃洛伊·卡萨格兰德 (Eloy Casagrande) 一直被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-think-theyve-figured-out-who-slipknots-new-drummer-is-3600051">广泛猜测为前 Sepultura 打击乐手埃洛伊·卡萨格兰德 (Eloy Casagrande)</a> 。不久之后，活结在三月份的一篇帖子中暗示了该阵容的最新成员， <a href="https://www.nme.com/photos/music-photos/slipknot-tease-mystery-new-drummer-in-rehearsal-photo-3599624">并分享了一张破碎的鼓槌的照片，标题为“排练”</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3750967" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3750967" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3750967" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/corey-slipknot-2011@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/corey-slipknot-2011@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/corey-slipknot-2011@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/corey-slipknot-2011@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/corey-slipknot-2011@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/corey-slipknot-2011@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/corey-slipknot-2011@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3750967" class="wp-caption-text"> 2011 年，Corey Taylor 与 Slipknot 一起现场表演。图片来源：Frank Hoensch/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-announce-departure-of-drummer-jay-weinberg-3531261">继去年年底杰·温伯格令人震惊地被解雇后，</a>上周的亲密演出标志着活结乐队与卡萨格兰德的首场音乐会。这场亲密的演出是在打击乐手兼创始成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-clown-interview-tour-2024-tickets-new-material-3559353">肖恩·“小丑”·克拉汉 (Shawn &#39;Clown&#39; Crahan) 告诉<em>NME</em>乐队今年将“回归基本”以庆祝成立 25 周年之后举行的</a>。 “我们要回到基础。我准备再次踢大家的脸了！我准备再做一次100人的场地了！我已经准备好做一个能容纳500人的场地了……”</p><p>他们还将在今年冬天返回英国<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-announce-2024-uk-and-europe-25th-anniversary-tour-buy-tickets-3556964">，庆祝他们的首张同名专辑发行 25 周年</a>。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fslipknot-tickets%2Fartist%2F763913" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处</a>获取剩余门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-clown-interview-tour-2024-tickets-new-material-3559353">在接受<i>NME</i>采访时，谈到 Slipknot 2024 年的计划</a>，Crahan 表示：“我已经准备好摆脱过去，进入一个我知道需要成为的世界。例如，通常我们会有大约两年的时间和一年半的时间——我们不再这样做了。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/slipknot-have-confirmed-the-identity-of-their-new-drummer-3751953">Slipknot 确认其新鼓手身份的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
